  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the chilling atmosphere of <i>Slendrina Remake</i>, where every minute is a fight for survival. This first-person horror game invites you into a sinister cellar filled with mysteries, puzzles, and spine-tingling moments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to The Cellar</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a single but highly detailed location: the cellar. This maze of dark hallways and locked doors hides many secrets. Its oppressive atmosphere will keep you on edge from start to finish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f2abc78a77cc7b1ccc27a50839bfe67f.poster.avif?t=1742045197\" width=800 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f2abc78a77cc7b1ccc27a50839bfe67f.webm?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f2abc78a77cc7b1ccc27a50839bfe67f.mp4?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Keys, Books, and Candles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your salvation depends on finding crucial items. Keys unlock new areas, books and candles are essential for completing the ritual needed to banish Slendrina.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f89b72601edeb829ccb919488221095e.poster.avif?t=1742045197\" width=800 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f89b72601edeb829ccb919488221095e.webm?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f89b72601edeb829ccb919488221095e.mp4?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve Puzzles to Progress</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cellar presents various puzzles that block your access to critical items. These challenges will test your observation and logic, adding variety to your exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f98c5e32660a079a315ad0f73bfcce3b.poster.avif?t=1742045197\" width=800 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f98c5e32660a079a315ad0f73bfcce3b.webm?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f98c5e32660a079a315ad0f73bfcce3b.mp4?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Banish Slendrina</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no battles here, but the tension remains until the very end. To banish Slendrina, you must collect all the required items and place them correctly within a pentagram. Only then can you complete this eerie ritual and escape the cellar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/7465dd68d99b7e66b7222a6ea77bbb7f.poster.avif?t=1742045197\" width=620 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/7465dd68d99b7e66b7222a6ea77bbb7f.webm?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/7465dd68d99b7e66b7222a6ea77bbb7f.mp4?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An engaging item collection system involving keys, books, and candles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tense atmosphere crafted through sound and lighting..</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you find everything, uncover the cellar’s grim secrets, and complete the ritual to banish Slendrina? Test your courage in <i>Slendrina Remake</i>—if you dare.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the chilling atmosphere of <i>Slendrina Remake</i>, where every minute is a fight for survival. This first-person horror game invites you into a sinister cellar filled with mysteries, puzzles, and spine-tingling moments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to The Cellar</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a single but highly detailed location: the cellar. This maze of dark hallways and locked doors hides many secrets. Its oppressive atmosphere will keep you on edge from start to finish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f2abc78a77cc7b1ccc27a50839bfe67f.poster.avif?t=1742045197\" width=800 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f2abc78a77cc7b1ccc27a50839bfe67f.webm?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f2abc78a77cc7b1ccc27a50839bfe67f.mp4?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Keys, Books, and Candles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your salvation depends on finding crucial items. Keys unlock new areas, books and candles are essential for completing the ritual needed to banish Slendrina.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f89b72601edeb829ccb919488221095e.poster.avif?t=1742045197\" width=800 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f89b72601edeb829ccb919488221095e.webm?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f89b72601edeb829ccb919488221095e.mp4?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve Puzzles to Progress</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cellar presents various puzzles that block your access to critical items. These challenges will test your observation and logic, adding variety to your exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f98c5e32660a079a315ad0f73bfcce3b.poster.avif?t=1742045197\" width=800 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f98c5e32660a079a315ad0f73bfcce3b.webm?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/f98c5e32660a079a315ad0f73bfcce3b.mp4?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Banish Slendrina</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no battles here, but the tension remains until the very end. To banish Slendrina, you must collect all the required items and place them correctly within a pentagram. Only then can you complete this eerie ritual and escape the cellar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/7465dd68d99b7e66b7222a6ea77bbb7f.poster.avif?t=1742045197\" width=620 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/7465dd68d99b7e66b7222a6ea77bbb7f.webm?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768100/extras/7465dd68d99b7e66b7222a6ea77bbb7f.mp4?t=1742045197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An engaging item collection system involving keys, books, and candles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tense atmosphere crafted through sound and lighting..</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you find everything, uncover the cellar’s grim secrets, and complete the ritual to banish Slendrina? Test your courage in <i>Slendrina Remake</i>—if you dare.</p>",
